This window (activity) is responsible for listing the songs, to choose from to play, along with the artist\'s names
        using ListView (by having an ImageView and two TextViews to form a template as shown in the activity) and link them adapters (or a custom adapter),
        along with the ability to transition between now playing, payment and artist list activities at the top.

This window (activity) is responsible for listing the artists, to choose one to show his/her songs,
        using ListView (by having an ImageView and TextView to form a template as shown in the activity) and link them adapters (or a custom adapter),
        along with the ability to transition between songs list, payment and now playing payment activities at the top.
